146
00:09:11,900 --> 00:09:13,800
Yes, take one.

147
00:09:13,800 --> 00:09:16,640
So beautiful. I'll buy it.

148
00:09:16,640 --> 00:09:18,200
Okay, thanks.

149
00:10:31,400 --> 00:10:34,040
Carlo, I just set afloat the lamp

150
00:10:34,040 --> 00:10:36,320
