182
00:12:19,720 --> 00:12:21,344
Oh, right.

183
00:12:22,120 --> 00:12:23,680
It is the Water Lantern Festival.

184
00:12:23,680 --> 00:12:24,960
Why did you know it too?

185
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:27,808
"Too"?

186
00:12:29,960 --> 00:12:31,640
